OL,3,CSelf-driving cars will be on UK roads
OL,4,Cin 2026, transport secretary says
OL,6,FSelf-driving cars that don't require
OL,7,Fmotorists to concentrate on the road
OL,8,Fwill be used in the UK from 2026, the
OL,9,Ftransport secretary confirmed.
OL,11,FMP Mark Harper said the technology has
OL,12,F"a huge number of potential uses"
OL,13,Fincluding boosting road safety and
OL,14,Fmaking it easier for disabled people
OL,15,Fto travel independently.
OL,17,FThe Automated Vehicles Bill to create
OL,18,Fa set of laws for using autonomous
OL,19,Fvehicles was introduced into
OL,20,FParliament last month.
